      "body" : "To fully uninstall the app from my phone, it was not enough to drag the app to the garbage can.  I also had to go into Settings &gt; Apps on my phone, find the app, tap the app, tap the &quot;...&quot; icon in the upper right corner of the &quot;App info&quot; page, and tap &quot;Uninstall for all users&quot;.  Then I was able to issue the <code>adb install</code> command succesfully."
