      "comment_id" : 30185204,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Or for a connected physical device, <code>adb -s DEVICESERIALNUMBER uninstall your.application.package.name</code>, where <code>DEVICESERIALNUMBER</code> can be found using <code>adb devices -l</code>."
