      "post_id" : 21868040,
      "comment_id" : 138793438,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "When you also add the <code>-t</code> flag, it fixes the error <code>Failure [INSTALL_FAILED_TEST_ONLY]</code> or <code>Failure [INSTALL_FAILED_TEST_ONLY: installPackageLI]</code>. These errors can happen when you do a manual upgrade of an app using <code>adb</code>. More info: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/25274296/adb-install-fails-with-install-failed-test-only#43654550\" title=\"adb install fails with install failed test only%2343654550\">stackoverflow.com/questions/25274296/&hellip;</a>"
    } ],
