    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can also consider adding <code>-d</code> flag to adb install. It should ignore this error.</p>\n\n<pre><code>adb install -r -d abc.apk\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
