    "creation_date" : 1426694400,
    "answer_id" : 29126851,
    "question_id" : 13808599,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>This error appears in my android project with multiple kind of gfx files. At the end no change in the manifest file was accepted.</p>\n\n<p>Because my lack of knowledge about the android devices I forget that my test device has a second User. This User also has an installed version of my app so I also have to delete the app for this user account and it works.</p>\n"
