    "last_edit_date" : 1724627462,
    "creation_date" : 1457101091,
    "answer_id" : 35798311,
    "question_id" : 13808599,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In Marshmallow, I got this error,</p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-none prettyprint-override\"><code>Installation error: INSTALL_FAILED_PERMISSION_MODEL_DOWNGRADE\nPlease check logcat output for more details.\nLaunch canceled!\n</code></pre>\n<p>Looking for solution I searched and came here.\nI deleted the app but still have this problem in Nexus 6. Later found that in,</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-none prettyprint-override\"><code>Settings &gt; Apps &gt; [My app name] have to removed for all user. \n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 93014,
      "reputation" : 4234,
      "user_id" : 254662,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 25,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/3e84fd4b4147b922e32b7b62cce3b41e?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
