    "question_id" : 13808599,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>I was having same problem. I was getting error when i tried to run in my android device <strong>not emulator</strong>.</p>\n\n<pre><code>sudo ionic run android \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>I am able to fix this by running </p>\n\n<pre><code>adb uninstall com.mypackage.name\n</code></pre>\n"
