    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>the thing that kept on killing me was that i didn't know that this app was installed for my guest account (although I had uninstalled it for the other accounts..)</p>\n\n<p>so i searched for the app in the app manager, and simply clicked on uninstall for all users</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/0QDUt.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/0QDUt.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a></p>\n"
