    "answer_id" : 65434060,
    "question_id" : 13808599,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I was having the same problem. I installed with</p>\n\n<pre class=\"lang-bash prettyprint-override\"><code>    adb shell pm install --user &lt;userId&gt; test.apk\n</code></pre>\n<p>For some reason, there was no icon on the screen. It was a debug build and all other consecutive installs were not working. Simply uninstalling the package helped.</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-bash prettyprint-override\"><code>     adb uninstall com.package.name\n</code></pre>\n"
